{"tid":1124523,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"今日番學有同學帶飯盒比我地笑到臉黃","createTime":"2019-04-25T05:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T08:23:05.000Z","uid":232639,"like":80,"dislike":1826,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"a696d06b834d21a7264bef5415a6f8816963d259","tid":1124523,"uid":232639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T05:43:47.000Z","msg":"是咁的，咁我地上Lecture堂放15分鐘break，<br />\n<br />\n咁打算成班friend出去食個Lunch chill一chill，<br />\n<br />\n有人提議食8&frac12; Otto e Mezzo BOMBANA，<br />\n<br />\n有人又話食L'Atelier de Jo&euml;l Robuchon，<br />\n<br />\n點知有個毒撚細細咁講話佢帶咗飯打算叮熱黎食，<br />\n<br />\n我地成班呆撚咗，<br />\n<br />\n之後笑撚咗出聲，<br />\n<br />\n大聲咁問：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「你五系窮到甘牙？」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢答：「唔...唔係呀，想草錢呀⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗買乜咁巴閉要草錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n之後我地搶咗佢個書包，<br />\n<br />\n拎個飯盒出黎打開個盒，<br />\n<br />\n將佢啲垃圾餸掉曬落垃圾桶，<br />\n<br />\n佢即刻衝上黎打鳩我地咁款不過比人㩒住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n<br />\n掉曬之後就咁掉番個空飯盒入佢袋，<br />\n<br />\n佢仲眼濕濕想喊咁，<br />\n<br />\n笑到我地仆街，<br />\n<br />\n之後我地成班人每人出少少請佢食錢好既。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好心你地班窮撚咪自己帶飯咁肉酸啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6971e52e24bc91344b4d71e19d6b91037b0a1450","tid":1124523,"uid":113922,"like":994,"dislike":8,"score":986,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T05:45:39.000Z","msg":"原來樓主細個咁樣俾人hey0過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62877ec81d3694fe929397ae248077c56c712511","tid":1124523,"uid":64